        "text_review_i6hpAW": {
          "type": "text_review",
          "settings": {
            "eyebrow": "ONE CAPSULE. REAL RESULTS.",
            "content": "P24 is a digestion wizard. I've always had trouble with my digestion, often experiencing bloat, brain fog and discomfort. Since taking P24 for the past two months",
            "author": "Lindsay E."
          }
        },
        "text_review_7A9p6E": {
          "type": "text_review",
          "settings": {
            "eyebrow": "ONE CAPSULE. REAL RESULTS.",
            "content": "As I (admittedly) get older, I find it more difficult to meet my daily protein needs. 120 grams seems like so much food! I love how this elevates some of the stress of hitting those goals",
            "author": "Theresa"
          }
        },
        "text_review_GgygCk": {
          "type": "text_review",
          "settings": {
            "eyebrow": "ONE CAPSULE. REAL RESULTS.",
            "content": "At my age (over 75) sleep doesn't always come easily. I also tend to have restless legs. Four weeks ago I started taking Amplifye and almost at once I was sleeping deeper with less leg pain. I also feel more alert in the morning. If my improvement in sleep and restless keeps I am sold Amplifye.",
            "author": "James C."
          }
        },
        "text_review_cLbEPV": {
          "type": "text_review",
          "settings": {
            "eyebrow": "ONE CAPSULE. REAL RESULTS.",
            "content": "I have been on a GLP-1 for a few months and you realize how difficult it is to consume anywhere near your DV of protein - this completely takes the pressure of because you feel like you are getting more out of what you can stomach in a day. Highly recommend",
            "author": "Max"
          }
        },
        "text_review_4zaCzM": {
          "type": "text_review",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "eyebrow": "ONE CAPSULE. REAL RESULTS.",
            "content": "As a long time athlete and one who has been training consistently for over 15 years, I had in some ways relinquished myself to accepting certain plateaus with my lifts. After taking Amplifye consistently this summer I found myself hitting new PRs on a number of crucial exercises. Furthermore, I’ve noticed my recovery time has been greatly reduced and am able to train an extra day or two per week!",
            "author": "Kiel"
          }
        },
